  "riddle": "1. Unearth the beginnings of a brand that soared from a basketball shoe to global prominence; in what year did this athletic giant take its first steps?\n\n2. What land, known for its lush rainforests and vibrant culture, boasts a name that signifies 'the island' in its most common tongue? Seek the height at which the ground sits above the sea.\n\n3. A city in the Pacific Northwest prides itself on its coffee culture and vibrant art scene. What are the coordinates in degrees of this urban hub that serves as the birthplace of the footwear titan?\n\n4. A curious elevation waits in the heart of the aforementioned city; how tall does the ground rise? Discover this height above sea level.\n\n5. Nearby, countless eateries satisfy the appetites of locals and travelers alike. Track down the number of restaurants that line the streets of this culinary haven.\n\n6. Combine the elevation you found in clue 4 with the count of eateries from clue 5. What new number emerges from their union?\n\n7. Southward lies a sprawling metropolis known for its film industry and iconic landmarks. How many museums decorate the vicinity around latitude 34.050?\n\n8. Transform the number of institutions discovered in clue 7 into a Roman numeral. How many characters does it take to express this symbolically?\n\n9. Seek the tale of a tech giant, born in a garage, who changed the way we interface with technology. What year marked the inception of this innovative company?\n\n10. Lastly, reveal the absolute difference when you add the year from clue 1 to the elevation from clue 4, and take that total modulo 10: compute (clue 1 + clue 4) % 10. The answer lies within a single digit, waiting to be uncovered.",
